<h1>Hi and welcome to this Index Page!</h1>

<p>
    I'll be uploading some cool images here :D
    
    -> From a file already in Rails's public folder
    <br/>
    <img src="/default.jpg"/>
    <hr/>
    
    -> From a file already on the web somewhere (fancy Google?)
    
    <hr/>
    
    -> Choose your file to upload!!
    <%= form_for @image do |f| %>
        Name: <%= f.text_field :name %> <br/>
        Image: <%= f.file_field :avatar %><br/>
        <%= f.submit %>
    <% end %>
    
</p>